FBIS4-50681 "drchi098_k_94003" FBIS-CHI-94-098 Daily Report 13 May 1994 NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political & Social State Council Appoints Two New Counsellors State Council Appoints Two New Counsellors OW2005104194 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 0603 GMT 13 May 94 OW2005104194 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service Chinese BFN [Text] Beijing, 13 May (XINHUA) -- Sheng Weitong (4141 3555 1749), deputy director and researcher of the China Forestry Institute under the Ministry of Forestry, and Wang Bingchen (3769 4426 1820), chief engineer and researcher of the department of hydrology of the Comprehensive Survey Institute under the Ministry of Construction, were recently hired by the State Council to serve as counsellors. On 27 April, they received letters of appointment signed by Premier Li Peng.
